Subject: [PATCH] ALSA: hda/hdmi - apply Skylake fix-ups to Broxton display codec
Git-commit: e2656412f2a7343ecfd13eb74bac0a6e6e9c5aad
References: boo#954647
Git-repo: git://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/tiwai/sound.git
Patch-mainline: Queued in subsystem maintainer repository

Broxton and Skylake have the same behavior on display audio. So this patch
applys Skylake fix-ups to Broxton.

Signed-off-by: Lu, Han <han.lu@intel.com>
Cc: <stable@vger.kernel.org>
Signed-off-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

